code: @Override protected void preSubmit() throws Exception {     verticesPath = createTempFile("vertices.txt", ConnectedComponentsData.getEnumeratingVertices(NUM_VERTICES)).     edgesPath = createTempFile("edges.txt", ConnectedComponentsData.getRandomOddEvenEdges(NUM_EDGES, NUM_VERTICES, SEED)).     resultPath = getTempFilePath("results"). }

@Override protected void testProgram() throws Exception {     ConnectedComponents.main(new String[] { "--vertices", verticesPath, "--edges", edgesPath, "--output", resultPath, "--iterations", "100" }). }
@Override protected void postSubmit() throws Exception {     for (BufferedReader reader : getResultReader(resultPath)) {         ConnectedComponentsData.checkOddEvenResult(reader).     } }
